title: S16 Ep50: Supernatural News/Parashare: Ouija Believe This Edition
itunes:title: Supernatural News/Parashare: Ouija Believe This Edition
description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News & ParaShare  Ouija Believe This Edition

Dave & Tim are visited by friends, actor, comedian and voice over god Carlos Alazraqui discusses his new Zombie Film, his paranormal experience and what it is like to voice some famous cartoon characters, Bill Chappell joins us to share his first hand encounter with a massive UFO sighting this past weekend, Creepy Ghost visitations, Baker Mayfield on UFOs & Bigfoot, White House Wraiths and a brand new Theater of the Mind!

Check out Witness Infection: www.witnessinfection.com

Visit Carlos Alazraqui on his Instagram: www.instagram.com/carlosalazraqui/
